observationText: The NCC-MPNST1-C1 cell line had a doubling time of 40 hours.
The NCC-MPNST1-C1 cell line exhibited rather weak invasive potential compared to other NCC-MPNST cell lines.
The NCC-MPNST1-C1 cell line harbored the potential to form spheroids.
The NCC-MPNST1-C1 cell line was classified into a group with NCC-MPNST4-C1 and NCC-MPNST5-C1 based on its sensitivity to certain anti-cancer agents.
The NCC-MPNST1-C1 cell line was derived from the original tumor tissue of a 37-year-old woman with NF1 who had a painful mass on her right posterior thigh.
